body:
### Welcome to SGI Engine's webpage!
SGI Engine (Superior Gaming Immersion) is an engine made by Arnau Bigas (@TheArni). And... yeah... I dunno what else I should write here. yay.

### Documentation
To check out the docs [click here](docs/index.html).

### Authors and Contributors
Thanks @Curly- (Sam Bazley) for helping me out with the engine!

### Support or Contact
For any issue you have please add an issue on GitHub. Please check the wiki or the documents first, since chances are your issue has already been solved!
